# fintech-ledger-system

## 🚀 Overview

A fintech backend system for managing accounts and transactions using a **ledger-based architecture**.  
Supports secure money transfers with **idempotency, JWT authentication, and ACID-compliant transactions**.

---

## 🧠 Key Features

- Ledger-based accounting (immutable records)
- Idempotent transactions (prevents duplicates)
- JWT authentication & secure logout
- Real-time balance calculation
- MongoDB transactions (ACID consistency)
- Email notifications for users

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB (Mongoose)
- JWT Authentication
- Nodemailer

